data.title: satcand: Orbital stability and tidal migration constraints for KOI exomoon candidates
data.name: satcand
data.description: Tools to apply theoretical constraints of orbital stability and tidal migration to KOI exomoon candidates.

evidence: "This is a repository for tools to apply known theoretical constraints of orbital stability and tidal migration to KOI exomoon candidates, which reproduce the figures in Quarles, Li, & Rosario-Franco (2020)."
"KOI_stab.py – produces Figure 1 from Quarles, Li, & Rosario-Franco (2020)" and similar bullets for Figures 2–4, indicating direct production of research figures/results.

"Included in this repository are: * KOI_stab.py ... * tidal_migration.py ... * SBO_tidal_tree.py ..." with no mention of packaging or registries, implying use via cloning the repository and running scripts from source.
